    <item>
      <title>赛诺菲首席财务官谈股票回购、研发和特朗普政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/sanofi-cfo-on-share-buyback-r-d-trump-administration-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赛诺菲首席财务官 François-Xavier Roger 在谈到研发前景时表示：“我们拥有非常强大的产品线。”在被问及美国新政府对疫苗的态度时，他补充说：“疫苗非常重要，我们将继续投资疫苗。”他在“彭博社：开盘交易”节目中接受了 Guy Johnson 的采访。此次采访于 1 月 30 日星期四进行。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/sanofi-cfo-on-share-buyback-r-d-trump-administration-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非再次停电，Eskom 连续 10 个月的停电记录宣告终结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/south-african-power-cuts-return-ending-eskom-s-10-month-streak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于发电机组故障，南非国有电力公司将自 3 月 26 日以来首次停电，结束了持续 10 个月的停电纪录。此次停电既为该电力公司赢得了赞誉，也引发了人们的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/south-african-power-cuts-return-ending-eskom-s-10-month-streak</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Eurazeo 联合首席执行官：欧洲需要简化监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/eurazeo-co-ceo-on-simplifying-regulation-in-europe-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[领先的欧洲私人市场资产管理公司 Eurazeo 的联席首席执行官表示，欧洲需要应对投资冲击，推进资本市场一体化并简化监管。William Kadouch-Chassaing 在戛纳 IPEM 会议间隙接受了彭博社的 Kriti Gupta 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/eurazeo-co-ceo-on-simplifying-regulation-in-europe-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应担忧持续，咖啡价格有望创两个月来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/coffee-set-for-biggest-jump-in-two-months-as-supply-fears-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场关注持续的供应短缺信号，纽约阿拉比卡咖啡期货有望创下自 11 月底以来的最大月度涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/coffee-set-for-biggest-jump-in-two-months-as-supply-fears-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:54:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行在盈利超出预期后开始新一轮回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/commerzbank-announces-400-million-share-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 宣布新一轮股票回购计划，并公布去年盈利创下纪录，以抵御意大利竞争对手联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 的主动收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/commerzbank-announces-400-million-share-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团预计数万亿美元将流入私募市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/blackstone-sees-trillions-from-rich-flowing-to-private-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石集团 (Blackstone Inc.) 一位高级董事总经理表示，随着富人能够更多地进入曾经由机构投资者主导的行业，私人市场将迎来数万亿美元的资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/blackstone-sees-trillions-from-rich-flowing-to-private-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:48:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
